snippet.title: CRAZY! Indonesia vs. China World Cup Qualifier Game!
snippet.description:
Indonesia vs China world cup qualifier 2025-- my first time at a professional football match here in Indonesia.

The venue was Gelora Bung Karno Main Stadium, (Jakarta) and it was packed to capacity at 80,000 people. Indonesia fans of the geruda (eagles) are known to be some of the liveliest supporters of Indonesia's national team.

I was really impressed that seemingly everyone in the audience was singing together, even before the game started. 3 full songs, and then the national anthem! It was an epic moment that has the power to give you goosebumps. 

My feeling is that the chanting, singing and passionate support of the fans has the power to boost the home team. Imagine playing a sport, with your country's flad on your shirt, as 80,000 people are going wild. The energy of the fans must translate into a swell of vigor in the players.

The crowd reached a new high when #10 Ole Romeny scored on a penalty kick to give Indonesia the lead 1-0 in the first half. It turned out to be the winning goal, as it was the only goal scored in the game.

The president of Indonesia, Prabowo Subianto was in attendance, and he congratulated the players, on the field, once the game was done. It goes to show you the level of importance, and national pride, this game had on every Indonesia citizen. Indonesians seem to be very proud and patriotic people!

After the game, the crowd sung a patriotic song, as the players walked around the field. Truly a memorable moment! It was fun to be a part of, with the stadium seemingly still full, even 20 minutes after the game ended. Awesome stuff.

THANKS FOR WATCHING!

TIMESTAMPS:
00:00 - 80,000 poeple wearing red (7 USD jersey purchase)
2:57 - Arrival at Gelora Bung Karno Main Stadium
5:10 - 3 songs, and THEN the national anthem!
8:03 - UNDER THE BANNER!
9:01 - Game start
10:56 - Ole Romeny: 2 close chances
11:33 - PENALTY KICK!
13:19 - Half time: 1-0 INDONESIA
14:11 - HIGHLIGHT: 2 great saves by our keeper
15:17 - China desperate for a goal
15:19 - INDONESIA WINS!
16:36 - Beautiful moment, patriotic song to end the game
18:29 - Indonesia through to the next round!

snippet.title: Watching Football In Indonesia Made Me Emotional (Indonesia vs China)
snippet.description:
Indonesia vs China World Cup Qualification
Watching Football in Indonesia - Watching Timnas live

In this video we will watch football in Indonesia. Indonesia vs China was the game, it was a world cup qualification match and one of the most unforgettable football matches I’ve ever experienced! In this football vlog, I take you inside the heart of the action at the iconic Jakarta Stadium, where the energy of the fans supporting the Indonesia national team (Timnas) was absolutely electric. This was my 2nd time watching football in Indonesia, and the atmosphere at the Jakarta Stadium left me completely overwhelmed with emotion, same as during my first visit at this stadium.

The passion for football in Jakarta, Indonesia is unmatched, and witnessing the Indonesia national team take on China was an unforgettable experience. This Indonesia football vlog showcases the insane fan culture, the chanting, and the unity that made this match special. If you’ve ever wondered what it’s like to experience a stadium visit in Jakarta, Indonesia, this video will take you right into the heart of the action.

The Indonesia vs China game wasn’t just about the sport - it was a celebration of the spirit of football in Indonesia. Whether you’re a fan of Timnas or just love an intense football vlog, this video is for you. The Jakarta Stadium and its incredible crowd made this one of the most emotional matches of my life. Football in Indonesia truly is a one-of-a-kind experience, and this Indonesia football vlog captures every unforgettable moment.

More Indonesia vlogs on my main channel @KenAbroad 

#jakarta #indonesia #kenabroad

snippet.title: Momen Presiden Prabowo Menyambut Langsung Skuad TIMNAS di Kediamannya
snippet.description:
#Prabowo #presidenprabowo #timnasindonesia #indonesia 

Jakarta — Presiden Prabowo Subianto menyambut langsung kedatangan para skuad Timnas Indonesia di depan pintu kediamannya, Kertanegara 4, Jakarta Selatan, Jumat (6/5). Ini adalah undangan khusus dari Presiden usai laga Indonesia kontra China di kualifikasi piala dunia 2026 yang berlangsung di Gelora Bung Karno, Kamis (5/6) malam.

Para pemain tersebut datang kompak mengenakan seragam merah-merah. Masuk paling awal adalah kapten Timnas, Jay Idzes, selanjutnya menyusul man of the match, Ole Romeny, si tangguh di bawah mistar gawang Emil Audero Mulyadi dan si penjaga barisan belakang, Rizky Ridho. Dan pemain lainnya menyusul masuk bersamaan dengan para official team. 

"Halo Jay! Halo, Romeny," kata Prabowo menepuk-nepuk bahu sang pencetak gol di laga malam tadi. 

Satu persatu pemain dan official disalami Prabowo tanpa terkecuali. Tampak raut wajah bahagia mengiringi mereka. 

"Sebagian silakan duduk," kata Prabowo. 

Untuk diketahui dalam pertandingan tadi malam, Timnas berhasil membungkam China dengan kemenangan 1:0. Prabowo sendiri hadir langsung di GBK, memberikan suport sejak awal pertandingan. Bahkan di penghujung laga, ia masuk ke lapangan, memberikan ucapan selamat, menyalami satu persatu pemain dan berfoto bersama.
